{
  "_comment": "Wimba image provider registry. Each model: picker meta (label/sublabel/icon), feature support, cogs_usd (cheapest aggregator = Wimba COGS, drives credit banner via credit_cost), and an ordered failover chain [cheapest aggregator -> 2nd -> first-party source]. Runtime: try chain[i] with 1 call + 1 retry; on failure advance. Providers keyed to adapters in image_providers.py; API keys = Railway env (see _env). Slugs per provider from ~/docs/wimba-image-providers-adapter-spec.md (2026-06-28).",
